WEBVTT

00:02:27.560 --> 00:02:30.736
I had the pleasure
of meeting Leah a few years back.

00:02:30.760 --> 00:02:34.040
She's a female and she has
a wife and a child.

00:02:34.920 --> 00:02:37.856
See, Leah was also assigned male at birth

00:02:37.880 --> 00:02:41.696
and she knew since she was a young child
that she was not a male,

00:02:41.720 --> 00:02:42.920
that she was a female.

00:02:43.720 --> 00:02:46.856
She hid it from herself
and from everyone she knew,

00:02:46.880 --> 00:02:49.496
especially from her wife,
until the age of 50.

00:02:49.520 --> 00:02:50.936
She couldn't take it anymore.

00:02:50.960 --> 00:02:53.056
She was like, I can't
keep living like this.

00:02:53.080 --> 00:02:54.296
I gotta get honest.

00:02:54.320 --> 00:02:56.976
She was extremely scared to tell her wife.

00:02:57.000 --> 00:02:58.256
What if her wife said,

00:02:58.280 --> 00:03:01.000
"This is unacceptable,
I want a divorce, get out"?